      "writtenOn": "2018-03-13T22:59:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ug actually no, this is not what we want.  It returns specifically: 1970-01-01T00:00:00Z.\n\nUnix epoch is kind of arbitrary.  Leaving it as zero time.Time would\u0027ve been more useful, but, eh :/.  Anyways I\u0027m leaving this as is because it does the wrong behavior otherwise.",
